  <p>Return the directory in the package that contains header files.</p>
<p>Extension modules that need to compile against mpi4py should use
this function to locate the appropriate include directory. Using
Python distutils (or perhaps NumPy distutils):</p>
<pre class="rst-literal-block">
import mpi4py
Extension('extension_name', ...
          include_dirs=[..., mpi4py.get_include()])
